- Book entity : title, author, published date, description, isbn 10, isbn 13, page count, language
- UserBook entity : added date, deleted date, book fk, user fk, read date 
- Book add (client/server)
- Book list (client/server)
- Barcode scanning for ISBN (cf. https://code.google.com/p/zxing/wiki/ScanningFromWebPages)
- Google API to fetch book data (cf. https://developers.google.com/books/docs/v1/getting_started)
- Fallback to isbndb, Amazon API, ...
- Share book lists
- Goodreads import